      • initializePossibleMoves

        public void initializePossibleMoves()
        This method initializes the possible moves for the inputed initial game state and game constraints. NOTE: This method could be improved by spawning possible moves based on a game board of varying sizes. This one only accounts for the start state of 3 Missionaries, 3 Cannibals, and a 2 person boat.
